[normal]About us[bold]The NHS Confederation
[normal] represents all types of organisations that commission and provide NHS services. It is the only membership body to bring together and speak on behalf of the whole of the NHS.
[normal] 
[normal]Our 
[normal]urgent and 
[normal]emergency forum 
[normal]looks
[normal]  to inform and influence members, stakeholders, the media and parliament about the issues associated with responding to, and managing the rise of, unscheduled care. The forum 
[normal]brings together a wide range of members and partners, in order to share knowledge and
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]good practice. 
